    "text": "Neither did Jeroboam recover strength again in the days of Abijah: and the LORD struck him, and he died.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                "
